divs: Sighting DetailsI went online to ufo webcams on March 29 at approx. 8:45pm. I saw a streak of light over the buildings that looked different. I do not go to ufo webcams often so by no means am an expert of how things looked. I saved a picture of the streak of light. I watched it for a while. At around 9:30pm, I went back online and checked the webcam and the streak of light was now exiting the screen. I took another picture. I again watched for a while. I once again checked the webcam again at around 10 pm and this time I was shocked to see a line of round lights. I have no clue if webcam pictures are useful, acturate or even analyzable ( if that is a word); however, these lights were so intresting I wanted to share them. Oddly, ufo webcam site as no address to send the pictures you save. So I decided to send them here. I was online when I saw the objects. Webcam does not alow for motion, can only reset to refresh image. I felt intrigued and curious during the observation. Finaly I refreshed once and the lights were gone.
